<D>__{for your parents.}
<C>__{tess}
<D>__{oh. yes. i hope so.}
<A>__{one of the power twins gets out of the driver's side door and crosses in front of the car. tess starts moving away from the window.}
<C>__{owner}
<D>__{which one is it?}
